section.section:
"Emergency responder" includes a:
career or volunteer firefighter within this State;
career or volunteer emergency medical services provider, as defined in § 13-516 of the Education Article, within this State;
career or volunteer rescue squad member within this State;
county employee who is performing an emergency support function described in § 14-803(2)(b)(5)(ii) of this subtitle; and
law enforcement officer as defined in § 3-101 of this article.
